This is the ReadMe for the Machine Vision section of the report. The three files contained are:

camcalib2.py 
Pose Est Basic
Pose Estimate w arduino 
dualcamposedetect.py

The three pose detection codes require a camera calibration matrix to accurately identify angles. This is referred to as matrix K in the report. THe code used here is copied from https://automaticaddison.com/how-to-perform-pose-estimation-using-an-aruco-marker/


